@startuml
title DataInsight AI - State Diagram (Alert Lifecycle)
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> New : anomaly detected\nalert created

state New {
}
New --> Acknowledged : user acknowledges
New --> Suppressed : auto-suppress rule\n(or duplicate)

Acknowledged --> Investigating : assign owner / add notes
Investigating --> Resolved : root cause fixed\nmark resolved
Investigating --> New : recurrence detected\nre-open

Suppressed --> New : suppression expires\nand anomaly still present
Resolved --> [*] : close

@enduml
